g.aria-label:
To create your own login wallpaper: open pattern.svg and set its color to your prefered accent color (--accent), copy the entire pattern and paste it in this file (outside of the canvas) Then select it and click on Object > Pattern > Objects to Pattern. Leave it to the side, that was all we needed it for.
Then set the background color of the rectangle to the right to your preferred bg color (--dark). Create a duplicate and set its color to the Pattern (next to mesh gradient) we created above. Tweak it to your liking (I set X & Y scale to 0.293).Then duplicate it the pattern layer to make it bolder.
Export and upload it to an img host like imgur.com.
